cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with completing partial 3D shapes using deep neural networks and shape synthesis. This involves computer vision (cs.CV) techniques for processing 3D shapes, graphics (cs.GR) for generating new shapes, machine learning (cs.LG) for training the neural networks, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for the overall approach, and neural networks (cs.NE) for the specific methodology used.
